## v130: Conservative Budget for Small Teams
- Hypothesis: v65 (rank #1, 2.99) used 1 aligner + 3 miners in 4-agent mode
- More miners = more resources = more hearts = more alignment time
- v130: max_pressure = num//2 for <=4 agents, num-2 for 5+ agents
- v130 4-cog seed 1: 3.50 (up from 3.14 in v123, 1.38 in v124!)
- Also: v120 appeared at rank #2 (2.92, 7 matches) — from concurrent session!
